parsePdbCodes

protected List<String> parsePdbCodes(String pdbAccessions,
                                     String pdbMethods)
Parses the strings returned from the UniProt web service for the PDB codes, discarding any theoretical models for which there is no image available from PDBe website.

Parameters:
pdbAccessions - the PDB accessions. Note that we are assuming that any theoretical models come always first. FIXME this is not always true!
pdbMethods - the methods used to resolve the structures.
Returns:
a list of Strings (non-theoretical PDB codes), or null if none is returned by the web service or if all of them are theoretical models.
